description.Name: description
description.Value:
Geocaching HQ is hosting 31 Days of Geocaching to inspire people to get outside and geocache as many days as they can in the month of August. It's like an all-community streak challenge. Tag photos and videos on Twitter, Instagram, etc #31in31 to help celebrate this month long challenge. Here is our August 3rd!

Thanks for watching!

Previous video: August 3rd
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TYJ23oVzsLQ

Subscribe!: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=CacheContinuum

Visit the Geocaching Network channel at:
http://www.youtube.com/geocachingnetwork

Outro music provided by Kevin MacLeod - www.incompetech.com

Follow us on:

Twitter:
http://twitter.com/CacheContinuum

Facebook:
http://twitter.com/CacheContinuum

Google+:
http://plus.google.com/106002401436315618959
